fr.umlv.jphoto.cela.data
Interface Picture

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractPicture, TransitionObject
public interface Picture

This interface define how a picture is represents.
it allow us to see TransitionObject as pictures.
Most of methods define here use standard methods of File when we use an AbstractRoot.

long getPictureLastModifiedDate()
Returns the time that the file denoted by this abstract pathname was last modified.

Returns:
A long value representing the time the file was last modified, measured in milliseconds since the epoch (00:00:00 GMT, January 1, 1970), or 0L if the file does not exist or if an I/O error occurs
